Christian church in the Middle East are all intertwined
in the history, politics and culture of Syria. Fr. David Nazar, SJ, will speak on the situation in Syria that has
given rise to the conflict and the refugee crisis, as well
as the response of the church to the crisis. Fr. Nazar has
been the Provincial Superior of the Jesuits in Canada
