Pontifical Orientale Institute in Rome. Monday, January
25, 7:00 pm, Pastoral Outreach Center. <i>Information</i>,
<a href="mailto:pbowman@stjames-cathedral.org?subject=Identity and Crisis: Syria and Beyond">
